OL,5, Sports presenter Gary Lineker has won  
OL,6, his appeal against HMRC over a #4.9m   
OL,7, tax bill.                              
OL,9,FThe UK tax authority pursued the star  
OL,10,Fover taxes on income from both the BBC 
OL,11,Fand BT Sport from 2013 to 2014 and 2017
OL,12,Fto 2018.                               
OL,14,FLineker presents BBC's Match of the Day
OL,15,Fand used to also work for BT Sport.    
OL,17,FHMRC said he was an employee of both   
OL,18,Fbroadcasters but a judge has now ruled 
OL,19,Fhe was a freelancer and had contracts  
OL,20,Fwith both broadcasters.                
